### Capacitor (mobile wrapper) ###
# Native projects are generated via `npx cap add android|ios`. They are
# derived artefacts; only the configuration in package.json,
# capacitor.config.json, www/ and mobile/ is checked in.
node_modules/
android/
ios/
*.apk
*.aab
*.ipa
release.keystore
.gradle/

### Frontend build output (defensive — none today, but future-proof) ###
/out/
.next/
.eslintcache
.turbo/

### Mobile build intermediates (defensive — covered by android/ and ios/, ###
### but kept explicit so a fork that re-includes android/ still ignores  ###
### gigabytes of generated bytecode and Xcode DerivedData)               ###
android/app/build/
android/.gradle/
ios/DerivedData/
ios/App/Pods/
ios/App/App.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/
